data.description: Sitting on nearly 60 acres of rolling hills, woods, a stream and abundant wildlife this property offers both privacy and luxury. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms with a convenient floorplan that has an open living room and dining concept and a full walk-out basement making entertaining a breeze. Enjoy morning coffee or evening wine on your backdeck overlooking the entire countryside. This property was built to accommodate horse enthusiasts. Featuring an additional barn with six stalls, that also has heat, electricity and separate hook-ups for RV parking and leads to fenced in pastures for horses to roam. A variety of mature trees can be found on the property as well as deer, bear and other wildlife with a stream that runs through the property. This private property on a dead end street surely won't disappoint!
